The following is a list of monster body types for the set_body_type() efun.

*TYPE* is the name to use in the set_body_type() efun. 
IE: set_body_type("arachnid");

*Wielding Limbs* are the limbs that can wield weapons. 
So, the set_wielding_limbs() efun must contain one or more of these limbs.
IE: set_wielding_limbs(({"right pincer","left pincer"}));

*FATAL Body Parts* are the body parts that can receive fatal wounds.
These are for your information only. 
They are used for the combat message system.

*Other Body Parts* are the other parts of the body. 
These are for your information only. 
They are used for the combat message system.

TYPE : arachnid

Wielding Limbs   : right pincer, left pincer
FATAL Body Parts : head, abdomen
Other Body Parts :
right fore leg, left fore leg
right mid leg, left mid leg
right tertiary leg, left tertiary leg
right rear leg, left rear leg


TYPE : centaur

Wielding Limbs   : right hand;left hand
FATAL Body Parts : head
Other Body Parts :
right arm, left arm
right foreleg, right front hoof
left foreleg, left front hoof
right rear leg, right rear hoof
left rear leg, left rear hoof
tail

TYPE : equine

Wielding Limbs   : right front hoof, left front hoof
FATAL Body Parts : head
Other Body Parts :
right foreleg, left foreleg
right rear leg, right rear hoof
left rear leg, left rear hoof
tail

TYPE : dragon

Wielding Limbs   : right foreclaw, left foreclaw
FATAL Body Parts : head
Other Body Parts :
right foreleg, left foreleg
right rear leg, right rear claw
left rear leg, left rear claw
right wing, left wing
tail

TYPE : fowl

Wielding Limbs   : right claw, left claw
FATAL Body Parts : head
Other Body Parts :
right wing, left wing
right leg, left leg
beak, tail

TYPE : insectoid

Wielding Limbs   : right fore leg,left fore leg
FATAL Body Parts : head, abdomen
Other Body Parts :
right mid leg, left mid leg
right rear leg, left rear leg
right antennae, left antennae

TYPE : insectoid-winged

Wielding Limbs   : right fore leg,left fore leg
FATAL Body Parts : head, abdomen
Other Body Parts :
right mid leg, left mid leg
right rear leg, left rear leg
right antennae, left antennae
right wing, left wing

TYPE : merperson

Wielding Limbs   : left hand, right hand
FATAL Body Parts : head, tail
Other Body Parts :
right arm, left arm
fin

TYPE : quadruped

Wielding Limbs   : right forepaw, left forepaw
FATAL Body Parts : head
Other Body Parts :
right foreleg, left foreleg
right rear leg, right rear paw
left rear leg, left rear paw

TYPE : snake 

Wielding Limbs   : mouth
FATAL Body Parts : head
Other Body Parts :
tail, torso


If you wish to have another body type added, please send mail
to Melnmarn with a similar layout of the different body parts,
we will see if we can add them to the list.

Melnmarn@ShadowGate
